---
title: Pesto & Walnut Panko Cavatappi with Blistered Grape Tomatoes, Asparagus & Parmesan
description: For Mother’s Day, we whipped up a bright bowl of spring flavors ready to please any mom in your life (in just 20 minutes!). You’ll toss twisty cavatappi pasta with asparagus and blistered grape tomatoes in a spring-tastic creamy pesto sauce, then sprinkle with a crispy toasted walnut panko topping and Parmesan for an elevated touch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66019431da283ecbc2883bca-78713f7e.jpeg
